Host *
    AddKeysToAgent ask
    AddressFamily inet
    Compression yes
    ControlMaster auto
    ControlPersist 60s
    ForwardAgent yes
    LogLevel ERROR
    PreferredAuthentications publickey
    ServerAliveInterval 60
    StrictHostKeyChecking no
    UserKnownHostsFile /dev/null

Host GitHub
    HostName github.com
    User git
    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/github
    IdentitiesOnly yes


